Package: ggseg.docs
Title: pkgdown Template and Utilities for the ggsegverse Ecosystem
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel",
           email = "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
    )
Description: Shared pkgdown template providing consistent branding across all
    ggsegverse packages. Includes the ggseg color palette, typography (Inter +
    JetBrains Mono), dark-mode support, a custom footer linking back to the
    ggsegverse website, and a build wrapper that enforces template settings.
